    </p>

    \[
    \begin{aligned} 
    \lambda_e &= \frac{\lambda_i\mu_2-\mu_i\lambda_2}{\lambda_1\mu_2-\lambda_2\mu_1},\\
    \mu_e &= \frac{\lambda_1\mu_i-\lambda_i\mu_1}{\lambda_1\mu_2-\lambda_2\mu_1}
    \end{aligned} 
    \]

